 server.<br>It might be interesting to have a casual server as well.  Maybe one with no high end encounters.  Make everything doable by 2 or 3 groups at most but remove all the &quot;uber&quot; items.  A lot of people, like myself, could care less about being uber, we just want to experiance the content and not have to dedicate our lives to the game. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uforin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Forin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Noble Squire</span><br>  Posts: 16<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(4/11/02 2:46:09 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=15249.topic&index=1>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Easy way for VI to change anything they want</span><hr size=1> Well said. <p><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>Forin Ironshield</B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Ariel" SIZE=1>Paladin of Underfoot<BR>Aegis Wolves<BR><BR>Master Smith, Master Fletcher<BR><I>"Animals die, friends die and I shall die.  But one thing never dies...<BR>and that is the reputation we leave behind at our deaths.</I></FONT></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ugreydon.showPublicProfile?language=EN>greydon</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ineffective.net/images/smilies/icon_04.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Noble Squire</span><br>  Posts: 18<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(4/11/02 7:20:00 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?top